    "\"Defining the boundaries to preserve the 'Chill'.\"" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "„Grenzen setzen, um das Chill zu bewahren.“"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Defining the boundaries to preserve the 'Chill'.\""
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Poner límites para conservar ese Chill.\""
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "« Poser des limites pour préserver le Chill. »"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「『チル』を維持するための境界線を定義する。」"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"'냉기'를 보존하기 위한 경계를 정의합니다.\""
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“划清边界，守住那份 Chill。”"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「劃清界線，守住那份 Chill。」"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"I do my best thinking out loud.\"" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "„Ich denke am besten, wenn ich laut spreche.“"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"I do my best thinking out loud.\""
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Pienso mejor cuando hablo en voz alta.\""
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Je réfléchis mieux à voix haute.\""
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「声に出して話しているときが、一番よく考えられる。」"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"나는 소리 내어 말할 때 가장 잘 생각할 수 있다.\""
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“把想法说出来的时候，我最能想清楚。”"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「把想法說出來的時候，我最能想清楚。」"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"I have the idea, but I can't find the words.\"" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "„Ich habe die Idee, aber mir fehlen die Worte.“"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"I have the idea, but I can't find the words.\""
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Tengo la idea, pero no encuentro las palabras.\""
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"J'ai l'idée, mais je ne trouve pas les mots.\""
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「アイデアはあるけど、言葉が見つからない。」"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"아이디어는 있지만 단어를 찾을 수 없습니다.\""
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“我有想法，却不知道该怎么说出来。”"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「我有想法，卻不知道該怎麼說出來。」"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"I want to keep making, not babysit a system.\"" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "„Ich will weiter etwas schaffen, nicht ein System babysitten.“"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"I want to keep making, not babysit a system.\""
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Quiero seguir creando, no estar pendiente de un sistema todo el tiempo.\""
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Je veux continuer à créer, pas passer mon temps à surveiller un système.\""
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「作り続けたいのであって、システムの面倒を見たいわけじゃない。」"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"나는 시스템을 계속 돌보는 게 아니라, 계속 만들고 싶다.\""
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“我想一直创作，不想天天伺候一个系统。”"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「我想一直創作，不想天天伺候一個系統。」"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"Ideas show up in fragments. I need to catch them before they vanish.\"" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "„Ideen tauchen in Fragmenten auf. Ich muss sie festhalten, bevor sie verschwinden.“"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Ideas show up in fragments. I need to catch them before they vanish.\""
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Las ideas aparecen en fragmentos. Tengo que atraparlas antes de que desaparezcan.\""
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Les idées arrivent par fragments. Il faut que je les attrape avant qu'elles ne disparaissent.\""
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「アイデアは断片のまま現れる。消えてしまう前につかまえないといけない。」"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"아이디어는 조각처럼 떠오른다. 사라지기 전에 붙잡아야 한다.\""
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“灵感总是零零碎碎地冒出来，我得在它消失前抓住它。”"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「靈感總是零零碎碎地冒出來，我得在它消失前抓住它。」"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"Life is too short to adjust margins.\"" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "„Das Leben ist zu kurz, um an Rändern herumzuschieben.“"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Life is too short to adjust margins.\""
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"La vida es demasiado corta para ajustar los márgenes\"."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"La vie est trop courte pour ajuster les marges.\""
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「マージンを調整するには人生は短すぎる。」"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"여백을 조정하기에는 인생이 너무 짧습니다.\""
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“人生苦短，别把时间花在调页边距上。”"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「人生苦短，別把時間花在調頁邊距上。」"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"My thoughts run faster than my fingers.\"" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "„Meine Gedanken laufen schneller als meine Finger.“"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"My thoughts run faster than my fingers.\""
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Mis pensamientos corren más rápido que mis dedos.\""
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Mes pensées courent plus vite que mes doigts.\""
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「私の思考は指よりも速く動きます。」"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"내 생각은 손가락보다 빠르게 움직인다.\""
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“我的思绪跑得比我的手指还快。”"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“我的思緒跑得比我的手指還快。”"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"Talk helps untangle thoughts.\"" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "„Reden hilft, Gedanken zu entwirren.“"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Talk helps untangle thoughts.\""
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Hablar ayuda a desenredar los pensamientos\"."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Parler aide à démêler les pensées.\""
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「話すことは考えを解きほぐすのに役立ちます。」"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"대화는 생각을 푸는 데 도움이 됩니다.\""
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“谈话有助于理清思绪。”"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“談話有助於理清思緒。”"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"The first version of a good idea is usually messy.\"" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "„Die erste Version einer guten Idee ist meistens chaotisch.“"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"The first version of a good idea is usually messy.\""
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"La primera versión de una buena idea casi siempre es un caos.\""
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"La première version d'une bonne idée est souvent brouillonne.\""
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「良いアイデアの最初の形は、たいてい散らかっている。」"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"좋은 아이디어의 첫 버전은 보통 엉성하다.\""
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“一个好点子的第一个版本，通常都是乱糟糟的。”"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「一個好點子的第一個版本，通常都是亂糟糟的。」"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"The product thought hits while I am walking, debugging, or switching contexts.\"" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "„Die Produktidee kommt mir, während ich gehe, debugge oder gerade den Kontext wechsle.“"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"The product thought hits while I am walking, debugging, or switching contexts.\""
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"La idea de producto me llega mientras camino, depuro o cambio de contexto.\""
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"L'idée produit me vient pendant que je marche, que je débogue ou que je change de contexte.\""
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「プロダクトのアイデアは、歩いているときやデバッグ中、あるいは別の作業に切り替えている最中にふと浮かぶ。」"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"제품 아이디어는 걷는 중이거나, 디버깅 중이거나, 맥락을 전환하는 순간에 불쑥 떠오른다.\""
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“产品上的想法，总会在我走路、调试，或者切换任务的时候突然冒出来。”"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「產品上的想法，總會在我走路、除錯，或切換任務的時候突然冒出來。」"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"Typing is unnatural; Speaking is instinct.\"" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "„Tippen ist unnatürlich; Sprechen ist Instinkt.“"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Typing is unnatural; Speaking is instinct.\""
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Escribir no es natural; hablar es instinto\"."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Taper n'est pas naturel ; parler est un instinct.\""
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「タイピングは不自然だが、話すのは本能だ。」"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"타이핑은 부자연스럽고 말하는 것은 본능이다.\""
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“打字是不自然的；说话是本能。”"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“打字是不自然的；說話是本能。”"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "**The Friction:** Typing too early pushes you into editing mode when what you really need is momentum." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**The Friction:** Typing too early pushes you into editing mode when what you really need is momentum."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**The Friction:** Typing too early pushes you into editing mode when what you really need is momentum."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**The Friction:** Typing too early pushes you into editing mode when what you really need is momentum."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
