    "Everyone in the cafe looks busy, but half of them are probably just switching between apps and feeling guilty." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Im Café wirken alle beschäftigt, aber die Hälfte wechselt wahrscheinlich nur zwischen Apps hin und her und fühlt sich dabei schuldig."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Everyone in the cafe looks busy, but half of them are probably just switching between apps and feeling guilty."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "En la cafetería todo el mundo parece ocupado, pero probablemente la mitad solo esté saltando entre apps y sintiéndose culpable."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dans le café, tout le monde a l’air débordé, mais la moitié jongle sans doute entre des applis en culpabilisant."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "カフェにいる人はみんな忙しそうに見えるけれど、その半分はただアプリを行き来して、罪悪感を抱えているだけかもしれない。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "카페에 있는 사람들은 다 바빠 보이지만, 절반은 아마 앱만 이리저리 바꾸며 괜히 죄책감을 느끼고 있을지도 모른다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "咖啡店里每个人看起来都很忙，但其中一半人大概只是在不同 App 之间切来切去，然后默默焦虑。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "咖啡店裡每個人看起來都很忙，但其中一半人大概只是在不同 App 之間切來切去，然後默默焦慮。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
